2008-09-30  eliz  <eliz>

	* build_w32.bat (GCCBuild): Use "-gdwarf-2 -g3" instead of 	"-gstabs+ -ggdb3".

	* w32/subproc/build.bat (GCCBuild): Likewise.

2008-09-30  eliz  <eliz>

	* job.c (construct_command_argv_internal): Avoid extra backslash 	in batch-mode Unixy shells.  Under DB_JOBS, display the contents 	of the batch file.

2008-05-31  eliz  <eliz>

	*** empty log message ***

