	Make sure to assign a boolean value to a 1-bit bitfield.  Reported on the bug-make mailing list.

	Fix Savannah bug # 14527: remember to free temporary line constructor
	memory if the line is empty.

2005-08-31  psmith  <psmith>

	Try using POSIX::getcwd to find the working directory wherever it exists. This should help the tests run more accurately on Windows (hopefully...)

2005-08-29  psmith  <psmith>

	Preserve the backslash that's printed by echo.

