2005-06-27  psmith  <psmith>

	Cleaned up some problems found with the tests running on a powerful Solaris system with an EMC NFS storage solution.  Still get some odd errors here unfortunately related to sub-second timestamps that I just can't figure out.  It all works if we run the tests in /tmp instead though :-/.

