1998-04-05  karl  <karl>

	(\dosetq): Use \normalturnoffactive instead of just \turnoffactive, so \'s in node names are handled properly. (\tie): Move definition to more rational position in the file. (\@, \{, etc.): Use decimal numbers in all cases, to avoid use of '. Paranoia only. (\+): Turn off once and for all at the beginning, and define as \tabalign in @tex.

