1998-02-25  karl  <karl>

	(\doprintindex): Change catcode of @ before \read, in case of \initial{@} being the line that is read. Reported by: Drew Csillag <drew_csillag@geocities.com>

1998-02-25  karl  <karl>

	(\dotable): Don't inherit \rightskip from surrounding environment.  Add \leftskip to \hsize in the first column.  Set \item to \crcr to avoid empty first row.  Prepend \parskip glue before table.  Set \everycr locally outside of alignment, don't reset it explicitly in \Emultitable. From Andreas Schwab.

	Also, work on leading commentary in file a bit.

