1997-07-05  karl  <karl>

	(\titlefonts): New macro to set title font styles, so italic etc. work in @title. (\titlefont): No longer needed. (\titlepage): Call \titlefonts instead of \titlefont. (\chapsf, \ssecsy, \ssecttsl): Correct magstep values. From: Stephen Gildea <gildea@intouchsys.com>.

