1997-06-18  karl  <karl>

	(\oddfootingxxx), (\onepageout): Leave space for the footline if present. (\everyfootingxxx, \everyheadingxxx): Call \oddfootingxxx and \evenfootingxxx instead of repeating their code. From: Stephen Gildea <gildea@intouchsys.com>.

	(\setfilename): Read texinfo.cnf if present.

	(\indexdummies, \indexnofonts): No-op additional commands @result @equiv
	@expansion @print @error @point.
	From: Dave Bodenstab <imdave@ais.net> (for texi2www doc).

