1996-11-19  karl  <karl>

	 (\deftypevarheader, \deftypevrheader): Remove 	* texinfo.tex (\deftypevarheader, \deftypevrheader): Remove         anything after the first space in the name to be indexed, for the 	sake of tzname[2]. 	(\dovarind): New macro. 	From: Andreas Schwab <schwab@issan.informatik.uni-dortmund.de>.

