1995-12-11  roland  <roland>

	[HAVE_D_NAMLEN]: Define this for __GNU_LIBRARY__ > 1. (D_NAMLEN): Macro removed. (FAKE_DIR_ENTRY): New macro. (dir_contents_file_exists_p): Test HAVE_D_NAMLEN instead of using D_NAMLEN. (read_dirstream): Return a struct dirent * for new glob interface. (init_dir): Function removed. (dir_setup_glob): New function.

