	Remove all [M_XENIX] code.

1995-12-11  roland  <roland>

	(main): Don't call init_dir.

1995-12-11  roland  <roland>

	Use plain stat instead of safe_stat. (find_semicolon): Function removed. (read_makefile): Don't use find_semicolon or remove_comments for rule lines. Use find_char_unquote directly and handle quoted comments properly. (multi_glob): Call dir_setup_glob on our glob_t and use GLOB_ALTDIRFUNC flag.

1995-12-11  roland  <roland>

	(safe_stat): Function removed.

1995-12-11  roland  <roland>

	Use plain stat instead of safe_stat.

