1995-08-01  roland  <roland>

	(child_execute_job): Close STDIN_FD and STDOUT_FD after dup'ing from them. Don't try to close all excess descriptors; getdtablesize might return a huge value.  Any open descriptors in the parent should have FD_CLOEXEC set.

