1995-01-15  roland  <roland>

	(start_job_command): Save and restore environ around vfork call. (search_path): Function #if 0'd out. (exec_command): Use execvp instead of search_path.

1995-01-15  roland  <roland>

	(variable_expand): Rewrote computed variable name and substitution reference handling to be simpler.  First expand the entire text between the parens if it contains any $s, then examine the result of that for subtitution references and do no further expansion while parsing them.

